---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - Aura Global Corporation" description="Human-Centric Innovation, Starting with Inventory Excellence. Learn about our mission to transform healthcare operations through trust, transparency, and technology.">

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="background: var(--bg-primary);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[var(--bg-primary)] to-[var(--bg-primary)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: var(--accent-glow);"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: var(--accent-glow);"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-padding max-w-[1440px] mx-auto relative z-10 py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 badge text-xs" id="hero-badge">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        Founded 2024
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-display font-black leading-tight" id="hero-title">
        <span class="block text-gradient">Human-Centric</span>
        <span class="block" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Innovation</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-display font-medium leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);" id="hero-subtitle">
        Starting with Inventory Excellence
      </p>

      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-muted);" id="hero-description">
        We solve real operational problems. No fluff. No buzzwords. Just technology that works for humans who work in healthcare.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4" id="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          Get Started
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/features" class="btn-secondary">
          Explore Features
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Brand Narrative -->
<section class="section-padding max-w-[1440px] mx-auto py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 animate-in">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--accent);">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: var(--bg-primary);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
            Born from Frustration
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
            Founded in 2024, Aura Global Corporation emerged from a simple observation: healthcare operations are drowning in chaos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
        <p>
          Hospital administrators wake up at 3 AM worrying about expired supplies worth lakhs sitting in storage. Equipment goes missing. Compliance audits create weeks of anxiety. The status quo isn't just inefficient‚Äîit's exhausting.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our approach is different. We call it <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Neuro Comfort</strong>‚Äîinterfaces that feel like a warm conversation, not a cold transaction. Combined with <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Cleanical Design</strong> (clean + clinical), we create software that healthcare professionals actually want to use.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl font-display font-semibold pt-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
          "We don't just build software; we build trust."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Triple Product Focus -->
<section class="section-padding max-w-[1440px] mx-auto py-20 lg:py-32" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
  <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-in">
    <span class="badge mb-4">Our Ecosystem</span>
    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-6" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
