        End the chaos. Track every item, predict shortages, eliminate waste, automate compliance. Built for hospitals who are tired of losing money to expired supplies.
      </p>
      <a href="/features" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-display font-semibold group" style="color: var(--accent);">
        Learn More
