      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
        GoEMR
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
        Electronic Medical Records that actually work. Lightning-fast, mobile-ready, and designed by doctors who've felt the pain of clunky EMR systems.
      </p>
      <a href="/features#goemr" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-display font-semibold group" style="color: var(--accent);">
        Coming Soon
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M13 7l5 5-5 5"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Product 3: Patient Portal -->
    <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 animate-in group hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.15);">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" style="color: var(--accent);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="badge text-xs">Coming Q4 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
        Patient Portal
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
        Empower patients with access to their health data. Book appointments, view records, message providers‚Äîall with enterprise-grade security and consumer-grade UX.
      </p>
      <a href="/features#patient-portal" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-display font-semibold group" style="color: var(--accent);">
        Coming Soon
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M13 7l5 5-5 5"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Product 4: Website Development -->
    <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 animate-in group hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300" style="border-color: var(--accent);">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--accent);">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" style="color: var(--bg-primary);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="badge badge-success text-xs">Available Today</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
        Professional Website Development
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
        Lightning-fast websites with FREE hosting. One-time payment, no monthly fees. Performance-obsessed, accessibility-first, future-proof technology.
      </p>
      <a href="/pricing#websites" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-display font-semibold group" style="color: var(--accent);">
        View Pricing
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M13 7l5 5-5 5"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Philosophy -->
<section class="section-padding max-w-[1440px] mx-auto py-20 lg:py-32">
