          For Websites
        </h3>
      </div>

      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color: var(--accent);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-display font-semibold" style="color: var(--text-primary);">One-Time Pricing</strong>
            <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: var(--text-muted);">Pay once, own forever. No surprise fees, no monthly subscriptions</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color: var(--accent);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-display font-semibold" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Performance Obsession</strong>
            <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: var(--text-muted);">Sub-500ms load times or we're not done. Your users deserve speed</p>
