          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="font-display font-semibold" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Accessibility as Standard</strong>
            <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: var(--text-muted);">WCAG 2.1 AA compliance included. Everyone deserves access</p>
