          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
            Rajesh Kumar
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-display font-medium mb-4" style="color: var(--accent);">
            Founder & CEO
          </p>
          <blockquote class="text-lg italic leading-relaxed mb-6 pl-4 border-l-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary); border-color: var(--accent);">
            "After watching my mother's hospital lose ‚Çπ12 lakhs in expired inventory in a single year, I knew there had to be a better way."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
